<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer7138204423745053120">Russell Conwell Hoban was an American expatriate writer. His works span many genres, including fantasy, science fiction, mainstream fiction, magical realism, poetry, and children&apos;s books. He lived in London, England, from 1969 until his death. (Wikipedia)</span>
  <span id="freeText7138204423745053120" style="display:none">Russell Conwell Hoban was an American expatriate writer. His works span many genres, including fantasy, science fiction, mainstream fiction, magical realism, poetry, and children's books. He lived in London, England, from 1969 until his death. (Wikipedia)</span>
